Insert a node in a BST

Link : https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/insert-a-node-in-a-bst/1?page=1&difficulty%5B%5D=0&category%5B%5D=Binary%2520Search%2520Tree&sortBy=submissions

class Solution {
    public Node insert(Node root, int key) {
        
        // Agar root null hai → matlab tree empty hai ya yaha insert karna hai
        // Naya node banao aur return kar do
        if(root == null){
            Node temp = new Node(key);
            return temp;
        }
        
        // Agar key chhota hai current node ke data se → left subtree me insert karo
        if(key < root.data) 
            root.left = insert(root.left, key);
        
        // Agar key bada hai current node ke data se → right subtree me insert karo
        if(key > root.data) 
            root.right = insert(root.right, key);
        
        // Root ko return karna zaruri hai taaki tree ka structure maintain rahe
        return root;
    }
}
